### Register User
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "user",
  "LastName": "2",
  "email": "user2@gmail.com",
  "role": "USER",
  "password": "user2",
  "profileImageURL": ""
}



### Login user
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user2@gmail.com",
  "password": "user2"
}

###

### Logout User
GET http://localhost:4000/auth/logout